### ==========================================
### SSO.Auth Server 測試
### Client Credentials + Refresh Token + Auth Code
### ==========================================

### ─── Client Credentials ──────────────────────
### 1. 取得 Access Token
POST https://localhost:7138/connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=client_credentials
&client_id=dotnet-webapi
&client_secret=LD8I1WziPQxReii6Kh5Ink+ViNtiaNfLwtqYLiVAMG0=
&scope=api

### 2. 用 Token 呼叫 UserInfo
GET https://localhost:7138/connect/userinfo
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### ─── Refresh Token 測試 ─────────────────────
### 步驟 A：先在瀏覽器取得授權碼，帶 offline_access scope
### 瀏覽器開啟：
###   https://localhost:7138/connect/authorize
###   ?client_id=blazor-wasm
###   &redirect_uri=http://localhost:5000/authentication/login-callback
###   &response_type=code
###   &scope=openid%20profile%20api%20offline_access
###   &state=test123
###   &code_challenge=TEST_CHALLENGE
###   &code_challenge_method=S256
###
### 步驟 B：用授權碼交換 Token（會得到 access_token + refresh_token）
###   將 <code> 和 <code_verifier> 替換為實際值
POST https://localhost:7138/connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=authorization_code
&client_id=blazor-wasm
&redirect_uri=http://localhost:5000/authentication/login-callback
&code=<code>
&code_verifier=TEST_CHALLENGE

### 步驟 C：用 refresh_token 換取新的 access_token
###   將 <refresh_token> 替換為步驟 B 回傳的 refresh_token
POST https://localhost:7138/connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=refresh_token
&client_id=blazor-wasm
&refresh_token=<refresh_token>

### 步驟 D：重複步驟 C（用舊的 refresh_token 再次請求 → 應失敗，token-rotation）
POST https://localhost:7138/connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=refresh_token
&client_id=blazor-wasm
&refresh_token=<old_refresh_token>

### ─── 授權端點快速連結 ────────────────────────
### （貼到瀏覽器）
GET https://localhost:7138/connect/authorize
    ?client_id=blazor-wasm
    &redirect_uri=http://localhost:5000/authentication/login-callback
    &response_type=code
    &scope=openid%20profile%20api%20offline_access
    &state=test-state
    &code_challenge=test_challenge
    &code_challenge_method=S256
